+## Live Demo ­ƒÜÇ
+
+- **Dashboard:** [http://192.168.178.86:8765/dashboard.html](http://192.168.178.86:8765/dashboard.html)
+- **URL Shortener (Flagship):** [http://192.168.179.250:3000](http://192.168.179.250:3000)
+
+Dashboard shows real-time worker progress, coin consumption, and time savings.
+
+---
+
+## Coin Budget Economics
+
+Bob CLI uses "coins" as compute budget. Foreman multiplies efficiency:
+
+| Scenario | Workers | Coins per Worker | Total Coins | Time | Sequential Time |
+|----------|---------|------------------|-------------|------|-----------------|
+| URL Shortener | 4 | 5 | 20 | 45 min | ~9 hours |
+| REST API | 3 | 8 | 24 | 1 hour | ~6 hours |
+| Full Stack App | 6 | 10 | 60 | 2 hours | ~15 hours |
+
+**Key insight:** Parallel execution trades coins for time. 4 workers at 5 coins each (20 total) deliver a complete app in under an hour.
+
+---
+
+## Components
+
+### Core Scripts
+- **`scripts/foreman-build.ps1`** - Main orchestrator. Estimates, spawns, waits, merges.
+- **`scripts/spawn-worker.ps1`** - Creates isolated git worktree, spawns Bob CLI instance.
+- **`scripts/merge-workers.ps1`** - Consolidates worker outputs into main branch.
+
+### Monitoring
+- **`status-server.cjs`** - Express server (port 3001) aggregating worker state from `.foreman/tasks/*.json` and `logs/*.json`.
+- **`dashboard/index.html`** - Live dashboard with progress bars, worker cards, coin counter.
+- **MCP Telegram Bot** - Sends 10-minute status updates to mobile.
+
+### Data
+- **`.foreman/tasks/*.json`** - Per-worker task metadata (status, coins, timestamps).
+- **`logs/*.json`** - Structured logs from Bob CLI instances.
+- **`worktrees/<task-id>/`** - Isolated git worktrees for each worker.
+
